description: Disassociates an Amazon FSx file system from the specified gateway. After the disassociation process finishes, the gateway can no longer access the Amazon FSx file system. This operation is only supported in the FSx File Gateway type.

parameters.name: FileSystemAssociationARN
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the file system association to be deleted.

nested_items.name: FileSystemAssociationARN
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the deleted file system association.
